      "source": [
        "Description\n",
        "輸入一串成績，每一筆成績皆以空格分隔，請計算此串成績的不及格數量。\n",
        "\n",
        "Input\n",
        "一串成績，每筆成績以空格分隔。(數字介於0到100)\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "Output\n",
        "此串成績中不及格的數量。(分數 < 60)。\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "dP__Vut-sxcx"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 1,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "Bm4d80g1sl88",
        "outputId": "a59c3f80-b1f8-493b-9266-e12427ce1e98"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "60 60 60 60 0 0 0 \n",
            "3\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "data = input().split()\n",
        "fail = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "for score in data:\n",
        "  s = int(score)\n",
        "\n",
        "  if s < 60:\n",
        "    fail = fail + 1\n",
        "\n",
        "print(fail)"
      ]
    }
  ]
